title: COMPOUNDS OF UNKNOWN CONSTITUTION
informative_references: Medicinal preparations containing materials or reaction products thereof with undetermined constitutionMedicinal preparations of undetermined constitution containing material from algae, lichens, fungi or plants, or derivatives thereof, e.g. traditional herbal medicines
definition_statement: This place covers: Organic compounds of unknown structure. That means the structure of the compound cannot be deduced to a level sufficient to classify the document in any of the other subclasses of  .

title: Lignin; Lignin derivatives
definition_statement: This place covers: Lignin and lignin derivatives of unknown structure, for instance the preparation or recovery of lignin from lignocellulosic material or black liquor.

title: Glycosides  (polysaccharides C08B)
definition_statement: This place covers: Glycosides of unknown structure

title: Alkaloids
informative_references: Medicinal preparations containing alkaloids with undetermined constitutionMedicinal preparations of undetermined constitution containing alkaloids from algae, lichens, fungi or plants, or derivatives thereof, e.g. traditional herbal medicines
definition_statement: This place covers: Alkaloids of unknown structure, e.g. isolation of structurally undefined alkaloids from plant material.

title: Ammonium bituminosulfonate, e.g. Ichthyol {also bituminasulfonic acid and its salts}
definition_statement: This place covers: Ammonium bituminosulfonates of unknown structure, e.g. Ichthyol
